high_descs: Turn around and face the black square table to your right.
Pick up the knife from the black table in front of you.
Turn right then face the white table to your left.
Slice the lettuce in front of you on the table.
Turn around and head towards the round black table.
Place the knife on a square plate on the round black table in front of you.
Turn around and head towards the white table to your right.
Grab a slice of lettuce from the table in front of you.
Turn around and head towards the round black table.
Place the slice of lettuce on the square plate in front of you.
Pick up the plate with knife and lettuce in front of you.
Turn around and head towards the black table in front of you.
Place the plate with the knife and lettuce on the black square table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a slice of lettuce on a black square table.

high_descs: Move to the small black table with shelves in the corner of the room.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Carry the knife to the head of lettuce on the right table, which is to the right of the small black table.
Use the knife to slice the head of lettuce.
Carry the knife to the round kitchen table.
Place the knife on the small tray in the center of the table.
Move back across the room to the sliced lettuce on the white table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the table.
Carry the lettuce slice to the round table where you left the knife.
Place the lettuce slice on the tray next to the knife.
Pick up the tray with the knife and lettuce on it.
Carry the tray, knife, and lettuce back to the small black table directly to the left of the white table.
Place the tray, lettuce, and knife on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Move lettuce to a tray on the black table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the door, then turn right and go to the black table.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn right and walk to the white table and face it.
Cut the lettuce into slices.
Turn left and walk to the door and then turn left again and walk to the round table.
Stick the knife on the tray point down.
Turn around and walk to the white table near the lettuce.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Turn around and take the lettuce to the round table.
Set the lettuce down next to the knife on the tray.
Pick up the tray with the knife and lettuce.
Turn around and take the tray to the black table.
Set the tray down on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of lettuce and the knife on a tray and set it on the black table.

high_descs: Turn and go to the table in the corner.
Pick up a knife on the table.
Turn and go to the white table.
Slice the vegetable on the white table.
Turn around and go to the round table.
Put the knife on the tray on the round table.
Turn around and go to the white table.
Pick up a slice of vegetable on the white table.
Turn around and go to the round table.
Put the slice of vegetable on the tray on the round table.
Pick up the tray on the round table.
Turn around and go to the table in the corner.
Put the tray on the table in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of vegetable on a tray.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the small black shelf on the right with a loaf of bread on it.
Pick up the knife that's next to the loaf of bread.
Move in front of the white table to the right and stand in front of the head of lettuce.
Cut the lettuce with the knife.
Turn around and walk to the black table with the another loaf of bread on it.
Put the knife on the plate that's next to the loaf of bread.
Move back to the white table and stand in front of the cut lettuce.
Pick up a piece of the cut lettuce.
Move back to the table with the knife on the plate.
Place the piece of lettuce on the plate.
Pick up the plate with the knife and the piece of lettuce.
Turn around and face the small black table that's against the wall on the left.
Put the plate down behind the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: To slice a piece of lettuce for a sandwich.

pick up the knife

slice the lettuce with the knife
turn around towards the table
drop the knife on a plate on the table
turn around towards the table

turn around towards the table
drop the slice on the plate

drop the plate on the shelf
anns.task_desc: drop a plate on the shelf with a knife with a slice of lettuce on it
